---
title: Crunchy Italian Chicken Sheet Pan Bake with Spiced Potatoes & Lemony Green Beans
description: Forget about that dusty old grill pan, that sous-vide machine you thought you might use “some time,” and that very specific hamburger patty mold: everything in this recipe is prepared on one baking sheet! Yep, all you have to do is pop it in the oven and wait for deliciousness to ensue. We’re talking Italian-spiced chicken, lemony green beans, and spiced, diced spuds. The best part (besides digging in)? Fewer pots and pans means quicker cleanup and more time enjoying your creation. That’s a weeknight win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/62965d8c4857ec39e506cad9-502787f4.jpg
